Package: dbc
Title: Install ADBC Drivers via dbc
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bryce", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "bryce@example.com")
Description: Wraps the dbc Go client API so ADBC drivers can be installed from
    R with dbc::install("snowflake").
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
Suggests:
    adbi,
    adbcdrivermanager,
    DBI
